# ===== TIA Portal — DO NOT ignore .zap19 (it is the tracked artifact) =====
# Live project working files (huge, machine-specific) are NOT committed.
# Only the archived .zap19 under src/ is committed.

# TIA temp / lock / autosave / per-user files
~$*
*.tmp
*.bak
*.lock
Logs/
TempFiles/
UserFiles/
System/
AdditionalFiles/
IM/
XRef/

# Other TIA archive formats not used in this repo (avoid accidental commits)
*.zap1[0-8]
*.zap2*

# ===== OS =====
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ===== Editors =====
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# ===== Local notes =====
/local/
*.local.md